snippet.title: Affection doesn't mean attraction ft. Amber-Paris
snippet.description:
Hey beautiful people! 

In this episode, we sit down with educator, storyteller, and lifelong learner Amber-Paris to unpack all the quotes and questions I've posted on my Instagram stories for the past few weeks. From soulmates and seduction to cafe culture and compatibility, we take a deep dive into the nuances of connections and building community. Listen until the end for some quick tips from Amber-Paris on how to elevate your life. Thank you so much for being in community with me!

Use the submission form on my website: www.theinxightspodcast.podbean.com
